Ferro Corp said it expects to reportsecond quarter earnings of about seven mln dlrs, or about 1.02dlrs a share, on sales of about 220.0 mln dlrs    In the year ago quarter, the maker of industrial specialtymaterials earned 5.1 mln dlrs or 75 cts a share on sales of185.1 mln dlrs.    Based on its current second quarter estimates, Ferro saidit will have earned 11.7 mln dlrs or two dlrs a share on salesof 425 mln dlrs for the six months ending June 30. In theyear-ago six-month period, Ferro earned 9.7 mln dlrs or 1.43dlrs a share on sales of 359.7 mln dlrs. Reuter&#3;